 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																									>Whose is the best roast potato recipe?</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>Last night an on-screen Jamie Oliver went to some lengths testing three types of roast spud. Our verdict? Lightweight! Here, our own Vicky Frost tests three varieties of spud with four sworn-by recipes from celebrity chefs. That's 12 lots of potatoes eaten selflessly, all for you. You may find the results surprising ...</p>
		
				
  	</div>
  	
