				<h1>Whose is the best roast potato recipe?</h1>
		   		    									This article was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2009-12-17T00:00GMT" pubdate>10.00 GMT on Thursday 17 December 2009</time>. 
					   	It was last modified at <time datetime="2009-12-17T10:54GMT">10.54 GMT on Thursday 17 December 2009</time>.
