					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>I cheat massively. I parboil until just before they disintegrate, allow them to steam dry, give them a gentle squeeze and finish them in a deep fat fryer at 170C. No-one has ever noticed, or complained: the outsides shatters like glass and the middles are fluffy and moist.</p>
						
