<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/08/22/DaiDawes/5ca9e1a0-77c2-47f1-b74e-097164592f5e/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
