<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/08/23/TheUkrainian/21c7e58b-1f20-42a0-9237-5acf3cc85002/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
