							<p>... and another thing... I've never had enough oil from the turkey or chicken or whatever to cook the potatoes, 'cos the meat is always in the oven at the same time as the pots. JO suggested cooking the meat early.. a turkey can "rest" for up to two hours (it looked pretty relaxed to me).. the obvious benefit is that you get the fat from the meat and an empty cooker to put your pots and veg in.
